  "description": "A small library that allows players to view into small inventories that lack GUIs, such as Armor Stands and Chiseled Bookshelves.",
  "body": "<table align=\"center\">\n    <tr>\n        <th>\n            <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/qsl\">\n                <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/v3/assets/cozy/requires/quilt-standard-libraries_64h.png\" width=\"311\" height=\"64\" title=\"QSL\" alt=\"QSL\">\n            </a>\n        </th>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n\n---\n\nInvPeek is a very simple library mod that allows players to \"peek\" into small, GUI-less inventories, such as Armor Stands and Bookshelves. It affects vanilla blocks/entities, and anyone can easily add support for their own mods! (documentation pending)\n\n---\n\n<table align=\"center\">\n    <tr>\n        <th><b>Join my Discord</b></th>\n        <th><b>Join my Ko-Fi!</b></th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <th><a href=\"https://discord.gg/f5dFYWX\"><img src=\"https://cammiescorner.dev/images/extras/discord.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" title=\"Cammie's Corner Discord\" alt=\"Cammie's Corner Discord\"></a></th>\n        <th><a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/camellias/tiers\"><img src=\"https://cammiescorner.dev/images/extras/kofi.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" title=\"Cammie's Corner Patreon\" alt=\"Cammie's Corner Patreon\"></a></th>\n    </tr>\n</table>",
